{"tid":2457652,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"因支持新疆被中國制裁  歐洲議員包瑞翰：但我還有台灣","createTime":"2021-03-22T22:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T02:37:32.000Z","uid":28765,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"44c9003536d3c6fe5adbbf7ea2630b7c154cf413","tid":2457652,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T22:40:01.000Z","msg":"〔國際新聞中心／綜合報導〕歐盟外交部長22日舉行會議，批准針對中國大規模拘留新疆維吾爾族人，制裁4名中共官員和新疆生產建設兵團公安局等實體。中國隨即反制，宣布制裁支持新疆人權議題的歐洲議會對中關係代表團團長包瑞翰（Reinhard Butikofer）等5名歐洲議會議員，不僅引發歐洲議會最大黨團人民黨主席韋柏（Manfred Weber）強烈抨擊，包瑞翰也推文表示，「中國領導人已經讓我知道，我將不被允許訪問（中國）大陸、香港或澳門，「但我還有台灣。」<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歐洲議會最大黨團、歐洲人民黨黨團（EPP Group）主席韋柏在「推特」發文表示，中國攻擊自由選舉產生的國會議員，顯示北京對民主的蔑視，歐洲不會畏縮，呼籲歐盟表態反對，並研擬反制措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3475636\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3475636&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXCcuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=f6232d11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3475636&h=58dcef11\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3475636</a>"},{"pid":"8396c1024134917159abef8f8dcf940ed6d35031","tid":2457652,"uid":42188,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T22:41:25.000Z","msg":"口交部：好嬲好嬲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b210f5b219c42b876a52b7e05f44f59a3311226","tid":2457652,"uid":19012,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T22:42:44.000Z","msg":"歐盟幾時先ban 廁所板同支那護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔想見到支那人出現在歐洲<br />\n<br />\n等我過幾年行去歐洲時可以唔駛見到支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji